The key to a flawless under eye starts with skin prep. I love using @topicals Faded Under Eye Masks to keep the under eye, hydrated and refreshed :)

#grammys #topicalspartner

Makeup by me on @cocojones 🤎 for the 2023 Grammys 

To create this sultry golden look on Coco I used a full face of @urbandecaycosmetics I used the quickie 24hr concealer for the under eye highlight, foundation, and contour to create the perfect full coverage flawless base. Products listed below 

Face 

* Foundation: Quickie concealer - 70wr 80wo 
* Concealer: Quickie concealer - 60nn 70nn 
*  Contour: Quickie concealer - 80nn 90wr 
* Stay Naked Trio 
* All Nighter Vitamin C Setting Spray
Eyes
* Eyeshadow: Naked Heat Palette , Naked Wild West Palette 
 * Eyeshadow primer
* 24/7 Glide on eyeliner - perversion, and demolition 
* 24/7 moon dust glitter eyeshadow - space cowboy 
* Perversion waterproof eye pen
* Subversion Lash Primer
* Perversion mascara 

Lips
* Vice Lipstick - oatmilk , 1993
* 24/7 Glide on eyeliner - whiskey 

#grammys#grammys2023#cocojones#Urbandecaypartner #udquickie

Anytime I’m working with a client I always  prioritize skin prep. It’s a necessity to get your make up to last all day and look as flawless as possible. I also always keep lotions and body oils in my kit as well. I’ve been recently using @kubrakayskincare and it’s become a staple in my kit ! 

For this look I used the Shea Butter Cream 
as a moisturizer.

I also used the hydrating body oil to make sure she was glowing from head to toe .
